    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《旗舰》是一款单人第三人称太空战舰模拟肉鸽游戏，从驱逐舰到战列舰，自由选择战舰并搭配装备，迎接基于节点的肉鸽挑战，每次冒险皆有所不同。你的战舰，装备，操作水平，随机应变的肉鸽流派都将会被不断挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激烈且有一定策略性的太空混战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/a285ed8be0a851c816db53ed7751bf73.poster.avif?t=1769962696\" width=800 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/a285ed8be0a851c816db53ed7751bf73.webm?t=1769962696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/a285ed8be0a851c816db53ed7751bf73.mp4?t=1769962696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人种类丰富，从战机到战列舰都将被你一一击破。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >炮火，激光，导弹，鱼雷，既是你要面对的威胁，也是你冒险中的最佳伙伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>肉鸽元素</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏都是独一无二的，你将获得新的特性，升级战舰，构建一个能够对抗宇宙威胁的强大战力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >科研系统则能永久增加能力，让下次冒险更加轻松</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >宇宙中的战舰模拟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/4fb6bf17a3c1ef3f55d8723aeab77c27.poster.avif?t=1769962696\" width=544 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/4fb6bf17a3c1ef3f55d8723aeab77c27.webm?t=1769962696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/4fb6bf17a3c1ef3f55d8723aeab77c27.mp4?t=1769962696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你所操控的不再是战机级别的小角色，而是一艘全副武装的战舰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战舰改造</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/bd2309d06c9dfb85911a35bf5cdc95c5.poster.avif?t=1769962696\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/bd2309d06c9dfb85911a35bf5cdc95c5.webm?t=1769962696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/bd2309d06c9dfb85911a35bf5cdc95c5.mp4?t=1769962696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏进程，你会解锁多种战舰以及战舰装备。你的每一个决策都将影响战舰的战斗力和战斗风格，让你在星际战斗中占据优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造自己的战舰，将会推出一定程度的战舰定制功能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras/3c4e3cf4a34b063bb17821d0626458aa.avif?t=1769962696\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/997090/extras_big/3c4e3cf4a34b063bb17821d0626458aa.avif?t=1769962696 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
